Note: 
It is assumed that you install openjdk latest revision:
[username:~/] sudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/java
[username:~/] sudo apt-get update
[username:~/] sudo apt-get install oracle-java8-installer
[username:~/] sudo apt-get install oracle-java8-set-default

to check java version: javac -version

To compile java code on linux, type: 
javac filename

To run java code on linux, type: 
java className 
for example:
java LinkList 
